  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate and analyse the clinical effect and application value of postoperative adjuvant
      TACE treatment in patients with different expression levels of CK18 using randomized
      controlled study and provide evidence for the necessity of postoperative adjuvant TACE.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
